original_title: 30 Minutes to Fitness Athletic Conditioning Volume 2
overview: Whether you are an athlete, a retired athlete still in training, or just want to train like one, Kelly Coffey-Meyer’s 30 Minutes to Fitness “Athletic Conditioning Volume 2” is your quick and complete full body challenge.  Workout One is a thorough program utilizing functional strength training in an easy to follow format. Your entire body will be pushed to the next level with a single pair of dumbbells. You won't use heavy weights, you won't be jumping endlessly, and there isn't an overabundance of repetitions.
title: 30 Minutes to Fitness Athletic Conditioning Volume 2
